x_938076_now_utils_now_utils_fix_scripts.description: Sets the reference qualifier (for Crypto Spec) based on the current selected crypto module and the proper display for the crypto spec field (should use alias, not crypto_module). This behavior was introduced in San Diego, but required this fix script for upgrade cases.
